  <description type="morphology">Stems 10–100 cm, minutely glandular-pilose distally. Leaf blades 2–3.5(–8.5) × 1–2(–4.4) cm. Pedicels 1–2(–3) cm, minutely glandular-pilose. Flowers: sepals 4–6 mm, to 9 mm in fruit; petals 4–7 mm, mostly exceeding sepals. Capsules 5–10 mm, usually slightly exceeding calyx. 2n = 20(?) (Asia), 28 (Europe, Asia), 29 (Europe).</description>
